    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You attach Chakra strings to yourself, controlling your body by nothing but your will. This technique can be used while paralyzed, and allows you to make a Concentration check (DC 20) each round to act as normal while suffering from that condition. Once the technique ends, it cannot be used again for 1d4 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n",
